# dot-np-directory check: running from a directory with no .np/ ancestor fires
# an error, cascades 13 skips, and exits 2.
# agent-instructions passes (CLAUDE.md present); git-ignore is NotApplicable
# (no .git directory), so 2 of 16 checks run.

! exec np admin doctor
stdout '.np/ directory'
stdout 'no .np/ directory found'
stdout '2 of 16 checks ran'
stdout '13 checks skipped \(cascade prerequisite failed\)'

-- CLAUDE.md --
Use np to manage issues. Run `np agent prime` for setup.
